==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: nosecount
<hw>nosecount</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A count of the number of persons
present or who are to be included in a group; <as>as, get a
<ex>nosecount</ex> of those who are planning to go</as>; also, a
periodic count of the population.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> census.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

